1797:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
1798:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        update the configuration at each commutation detection on the TRGI input of the Timer,
1799:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the typical use of this feature is with the use of another Timer(interface Timer)
