1800:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        configured in Hall sensor interface, this interface Timer will generate the
1801:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        commutation at its TRGO output (connected to Timer used in this function) each time
1802:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the TI1 of the Interface Timer detect a commutation at its input TI1.
