1810:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_NONE: No trigger is needed
1811:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  CommutationSource the Commutation Event source
1812:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
